We Know When You’ll Get Engaged Based On Your In-N-Out Order You got: Valentine’s Day, 2019 Congrats! You’re getting engaged on the most romantic day of the year. OMG!
You got: 4th of July, 2020 You definitely like a little patriotism with your hot cup of love. Congrats!
You got: Christmas Eve, 2017 You’re gonna get engaged in front of family and friends while Christmas music plays in the background. Mistletoe all around!
You got: New Year’s Eve, 2019 What better way to ring in the new year than to get engaged to your S.O. Congratulations!
You got: On Your Birthday in 2020 Yup! You’re gonna get engaged on your birthday, and it’ll be the best birthday present ever. Happy birthday and happy engagement!
You got: At Your Friend’s Wedding, 2019 For the love of Christ, DO NOT LET THIS HAPPEN. It’s rude. Don’t even think about it. Even if you get permission from the groom and bride, DON’T. YOU. DARE! They REALLY don’t want you to do it at their wedding. DON’T. FUCKING. DO. IT. You’ve been warned.
